EN: If you are interested, you can apply for this position.

ZH: 我会尽快应聘的。
EN: I will apply as soon as possible.

ZH: 你知道该如何应聘这个职位吗？
EN: Do you know how to apply for this position?

ZH: 他非常努力地准备了应聘面试。
EN: He prepared for the job interview diligently.

ZH: 我已经提交了应聘材料。
EN: I have submitted my application materials.

ZH: 他面试时展现出了优秀的应聘技巧。
EN: He displayed excellent job application skills during the interview.

